trans-unit.source: This project needs a new maintainer. I only ever managed to test it against a now ancient ClearCase 7.1 LT installation, to which I’m likely to lose access in a not too distant future.

trans-unit.source: It is being developed with Python 3.7 so as to be compatible with Python 2.7. Tests are run also with 3.4, 3.5 and 3.6.
